    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-dashed border-base-300 p-16 text-center fade-in">
        <span class="text-6xl block mb-6" aria-hidden="true">📸</span>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 text-base-content/70">活動回顧 — 即將更新</h1>
        <p class="text-base-content/50 mb-8">4/2 首場活動結束後，這裡會更新為完整回顧：<br />現場照片、參加者心得、重點摘要。</p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 justify-center flex-wrap">
          <a href="/events/001-first-meetup/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm text-primary border-primary">← 回活動詳情</a>
          <a href="/events/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm text-base-content/70 border-base-300">查看所有活動</a>
        </div>
      </div>

